name: Benjamin VELASQUEZ, Petitioner v. Hon. F.A. MASSIAH-JACKSON, President Judge Philadelphia County, Respondent

parties: Benjamin VELASQUEZ, Petitioner v. Hon. F.A. MASSIAH-JACKSON, President Judge Philadelphia County, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 23rd day of June, 2009, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the jurist’s name from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
